-- MOVES-Maya Bhandari joins Threadneedle Investments from Citigroup
-- 
-- Tue Sep 02, 2014 08:15AM EDT
-- None



Sept 2 (Reuters) - Threadneedle Investments, the investment management unit of Ameriprise Financial Inc <AMP.N>, appointed Maya Bhandari as investment strategist to its multi-asset allocation team.

Bhandari joins from Citigroup Inc <C.N>, where she was a director of global macro strategy & asset allocation.